## Failure Patterns (DIAGNOSE)

| Code | Pattern | Quick Fix |
|---|---|---|
| I01 | Instruction ignored | Hierarchy, XML tags, move up |
| I02 | Partial compliance | Prioritize, reduce constraints |
| F01 | Format drift | Format example start+end |
| F02 | Wrong format | Schema with example |
| H01 | Hallucination facts | "Use ONLY provided data" |
| H02 | Hallucination instructions | Scope boundaries |
| R01 | Repetition loop | Context_Anchor re-anchoring |
| R02 | Scope creep | Scope gate |
| T01 | Tone mismatch | Explicit tone contract |
| T02 | Verbosity explosion | Word count constraint |

