## Platform Rules

- **Claude**: XML tags, docs TOP query BOTTOM, extended thinking
- **GPT-4o**: Few-shot highest leverage, system prompt weak
- **o3**: SHORT, NO CoT, "Formatting re-enabled"
- **Gemini**: Instructions AFTER data, temp >= 1.0
- **DeepSeek R1**: NO system msg, NO few-shot, temp 0.5-0.7
